        public Chapter(java.util.UUID id,
       java.util.UUID storyId,
       java.lang.String text)
        Initialize a new chapter with an id. Can also be used to make a chapter from the chapter information retrieved from the database. Can also be used to create a choice that will serve to hold search criteria.
        Parameters:
        id - The unique id of the chapter
        storyId - The id of the story the chapter is from
        text - The chapter text that the user will be reading
